    <title>CINTA-TWO</title>
    <link href="/2023/10/05/CINTA-TWO/"/>
    <url>/2023/10/05/CINTA-TWO/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="编程题">编程题</h1><h2 id="模指数运算函数mod_exp">1.模指数运算函数Mod_Exp</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS 1</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//模指数运算</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Mod_Exp</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, b, m;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;输入a,b,m\n&quot;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d,%d,%d&quot;</span>, &amp;a, &amp;b, &amp;m);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;a的b次方模m的值为%d&quot;</span>, Mod_Exp(a, b, m));<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Mod_Exp</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (b &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((b &amp; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) res = (res * a) % m;<br>b /= <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>a = (a * a) % m;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="求乘法逆元的函数mul_inverse">2.求乘法逆元的函数Mul_Inverse</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS 1</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;cmath&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//求乘法逆元</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Mul_Inverse</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, m;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入a,m (a，m必须互素) \n&quot;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d,%d&quot;</span>, &amp;a, &amp;m);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;a模m的乘法逆元为%d&quot;</span>, Mul_Inverse(a, m));<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Mul_Inverse</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; m; i++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((a * i) % m == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>&#123;<br>res = i;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>&#125;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="计算题">计算题</h1><h2 id="section">4.1</h2><p><span class="math display">\[3^{2019}\equiv 3^{91*22+17}\ \ (mod\ 23)\]</span></p><p>因为2019 = 91*(23-1) + 17, 根据费马小定理： <spanclass="math display">\[3^{91*22+17}\ \  \equiv 3^{17}\ \ (mod\ 23)=3*3^{16}\ \ (mod\ 23)\]</span> 又因 <span class="math display">\[3^2\ \ mod\ \ 23 = 9\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[3^4\ \ mod\ 23 = 9*9\ \ mod\ 23 =12\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[3^8\ \ mod\ 23 = 12*12\ \ mod\ 23 =6\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[3^{16}\ \ mod\ 23 = 6*6\ \ mod\ 23 =13\]</span></p><p>故 <span class="math display">\[3^{17}\equiv 3*3^{16}\ \ (mod\ 13)=39\ \ mod\ 23=16\]</span> 综上： <span class="math display">\[3^{2019}\ mod\ 23 =16\]</span></p><h2 id="section-1">4.5</h2><p>即证： <span class="math display">\[2^{70}+3^{70}\equiv0\ (mod\ 13)\]</span> 根据费马小定理: <span class="math display">\[2^{70}\equiv2^{5*12+10}\ mod\ 13 =2^{10}\ mod\ 13\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[2^{5}\ mod\ 13 = 6\]</span></p><p>故 <span class="math display">\[2^{10}\ mod\ 13 = 6*6\ mod\ 13 =10\]</span> 同理: <span class="math display">\[3^{70}\equiv3^{5*12+10}\ mod\ 13 =3^{10}\ mod\ 13\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[3^{5}\ mod\ 13 = 9\]</span></p><p>故 <span class="math display">\[3^{10}\ mod\ 13 = 9*9\ mod\ 13 =3\]</span> 故 <span class="math display">\[2^{70}\equiv10\ mod\ 13\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[3^{70}\equiv3\ mod\ 13\]</span></p><p>有： <span class="math display">\[2^{70}+3^{70}\equiv13\ (mod\ 13) =0\ (mod\ 13)\]</span> Q.E.D</p><h2 id="section-2">4.6</h2><p>因为2与55互素，根据欧拉定理： <span class="math display">\[2^{\phi(55)}\equiv1\ (mod\ 55)\]</span> 而 <span class="math display">\[\phi(55)=\phi(5)*\phi(11)=4*10=40\]</span> 故有： <span class="math display">\[2^{40}\equiv1\ (mod\ 55)\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[2^{100000}\equiv2^{2500*40}\ \equiv2^{40}\equiv1\ mod\ 55\]</span></p><p>故 <span class="math display">\[2^{100000}\ mod\ 55 =1\]</span></p><h2 id="section-3">4.8</h2><p><span class="math display">\[该问等价于求: 7^{1000}\ mod\ 100\]</span></p><p>由于7和1000互素，根据欧拉定理： <span class="math display">\[7^{\phi(100)}\equiv1\ (mod\ 100)\]</span> 而 <span class="math display">\[\phi(100)=\phi(5^2)*\phi(2^2)=20*2=40\]</span> 故 <span class="math display">\[7^{40}\equiv1\ (mod\ 100)\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[7^{1000}\equiv7^{25*40}\equiv7^{40}\equiv1\ (mod\ 100)\]</span></p><p>故 <span class="math display">\[7^{1000}的最后两个数位为01\]</span></p>]]></content>
    
    
