    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="cinta-one">CINTA-ONE</h1><h1 id="迭代版本的简单乘法">1. 迭代版本的简单乘法</h1><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS 1</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 简单乘法</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">multiply1</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 简单乘法的第二种思路</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">multiply2</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 迭代version的简单乘法</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">multiply3</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 判断一个数是否为偶数</span><br><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Iseven</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> &#123;<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;乘积为：%d\n&quot;</span>, multiply1(<span class="hljs-number">19</span>, <span class="hljs-number">20</span>));<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;乘积为：%d\n&quot;</span>, multiply2(<span class="hljs-number">19</span>, <span class="hljs-number">20</span>));<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;乘积为：%d\n&quot;</span>, multiply3(<span class="hljs-number">19</span>, <span class="hljs-number">20</span>));<br><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">multiply1</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (b == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a + multiply1(a, b - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">multiply2</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; b; i++)<br>&#123;<br>res += a;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">multiply3</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (Iseven(b) == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; (b / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>); i++)<br>&#123;<br>res += a;<br>&#125;<br>res *= <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; (b / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>); i++)<br>&#123;<br>res += a;<br>&#125;<br>res *= <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>res += a;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Iseven</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (a % <span class="hljs-number">2</span> == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="证明除法算法">2. 证明除法算法</h1><h2 id="除法算法">2.1 除法算法</h2><p><strong>对任意给定的整数a和b，其中b &gt;0，存在唯一的整数对q（商）和r（余数）使得， </strong> <spanclass="math display">\[a = qb + r\]</span> <strong>且 0 ≤ r &lt; b。</strong></p><h2 id="证明过程">2.2 证明过程</h2><h3 id="证明存在性">2.2.1 证明存在性</h3><p>构造集合 <span class="math display">\[S = \{a-bk:k\in Z\ 且\  a-bk \ge 0 \}\]</span> 显然，集合S非空，由良序原则，存在一个最小元<spanclass="math display">\[r \in S\  且 \ r=a-qb\]</span></p><p>因此，<span class="math display">\[a = qb + r, r\ge 0\]</span></p><p>我们采用反证法，假设最小元r&gt;b，则</p><p><span class="math display">\[\exists t\in Z\   s.t.\ r = tb +r^*\]</span></p><p>则有 <span class="math display">\[a=qb+r=qb+tb+r^*=(q+t)b+r^*\]</span> 令 <span class="math display">\[ q+t = q^* \in Z\]</span> 则有<span class="math display">\[a=q^*b+r^*\]</span> <spanclass="math display">\[此时存在r^*&lt;r,则此时的最小元为r^*,与假设矛盾.\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[综上:0\leq r&lt; b\]</span></p><p>Q.E.D</p><h3 id="证明唯一性">2.2.2 证明唯一性</h3><p><spanclass="math display">\[我们才用反证法，假设存在两对(q_1,r_1)(q_2,r_2)\]</span>满足<span class="math display">\[a=qb+r\]</span> 其中<spanclass="math display">\[q_1\ne q_2,\ r_1\ne r_2,\ 0\leq r_1 &lt; b,\0\leq r_2 &lt; b\]</span>则有： <span class="math display">\[q_1b+r_1=q_2b+r_2\]</span> 处理得： <span class="math display">\[(q_1-q_2)b=(r_2-r_1)\]</span> 即 <span class="math display">\[b\mid(r_2-r_1)\\\]</span> 又 <span class="math display">\[\because 0\leq r_1 &lt; b,\ 0\leq r_2 &lt; b\\\]</span> <span class="math display">\[\therefore -b&lt;r_2-r_1&lt;b\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[\therefore r_2-r_1 = 0\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[与假设不符，故只存在一对(q,r)\ s.t.\0\leq r &lt; b\ 且\ a=qb+r\]</span></p><p>Q.E.D</p><h1 id="程序">3. 程序</h1><h2 id="迭代版本的gcd">3.1 迭代版本的gcd</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS 1</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">gcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, b;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入a,b\n&quot;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d,%d&quot;</span>,&amp;a,&amp;b);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;a和b最大公因数为：%d&quot;</span>, gcd(a, b));<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">gcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> temp;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (a &lt; b)<br>&#123;<br>temp = b;<br>b = a;<br>a = temp;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (a % b)<br>&#123;<br>temp = b;<br>b = a % b;<br>a = temp;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> b;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="迭代版本的egcd">3.2 迭代版本的egcd</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS 1</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ra+sb = gcd(a,b)</span><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">egcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, b;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入a,b\n&quot;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d,%d&quot;</span>, &amp;a, &amp;b);<br>egcd(a, b);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">egcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> s1 = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> r0 = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> s0 = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> r1 = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> q;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> temp;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res_r;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res_s;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res_gcd;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (b)<br>&#123;<br>q = a / b;<br>temp = a;<br>a = b;<br>b = temp % b;<br>temp = r0;<br>r0 = r1;<br>r1 = temp - q * r1;<br>temp = s0;<br>s0 = s1;<br>s1 = temp - q * s1;<br>&#125;<br>res_r = r0;<br>res_s = s0;<br>res_gcd = a;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;r=%d,s=%d,gcd(a,b)=%d&quot;</span>, res_r, res_s, res_gcd);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="基于gcd算法实现的函数">3.3 基于gcd算法实现的函数</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS 1</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">gcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入n\n&quot;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> count = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt; n; i++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (gcd(n, i) == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) count++;<br><br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, count);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">gcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> temp;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (a &lt; b)<br>&#123;<br>temp = b;<br>b = a;<br>a = temp;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (a % b)<br>&#123;<br>temp = b;<br>b = a % b;<br>a = temp;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> b;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="第二章的第68题">4. 第二章的第6、8题</h1><h2 id="第6题">4.1 第6题</h2><ul><li><span class="math display">\[假设g^a\equiv1\ (mod\ m)\ 且\ g^b\equiv1(mod\ m),请证明：g^{gcd(a,b)}\equiv 1(mod\ m).\]</span></li></ul><hr /><p>证明：</p><p><span class="math display">\[Ⅰ.当m\neq 1\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[由B\acute{e}zout定理可得：\]</span><span class="math display">\[gcd(a,b)=ar+bs\]</span> 且a与b的最大公因子是唯一的。</p><p>即证： <span class="math display">\[g^{ar＋bs}\equiv1(mod\ m)\\\]</span> 又 <span class="math display">\[g^a\equiv1\ (mod\ m)\ \Rightarrow\ g^a=k_1m+1\]</span> <span class="math display">\[g^b\equiv1\ (mod\ m)\ \Rightarrow\ g^b=k_2m+1\]</span></p><p>又 <span class="math display">\[g^a·g^b = (k_1m+1)·(k_2m+1)=k_1k_2m+k_1m+k_2m+1\\(g^a·g^b)\ mod\ m =(k_1k_2m^2+k_1m+k_2m+1)\ mod\ m =1\]</span> 故 <span class="math display">\[g^{a+b}\equiv1(mod\ m)\]</span> 接着证： <span class="math display">\[(g^a)^r\equiv 1(mod\ m)\\(g^b)^s\equiv 1(mod\ m)\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[\because(g^a)^r=(k_1m+1)^r=C_r^0(k_1m)^r1^0+C_r^1(k_1m)^{r-1}1^1+...+C_r^{r-1}(k_1m)^11^{r-1}+C_r^r(k_1m)^01^r\\\ \ \ \ \(g^b)^s=(k_2m+1)^s=C_s^0(k_2m)^s1^0+C_s^1(k_2m)^{s-1}1^1+...+C_s^{s-1}(k_2m)^11^{s-1}+C_s^s(k_2m)^01^s\\\]</span></p><p>显然， <span class="math display">\[[C_r^0(k_1m)^r1^0+C_r^1(k_1m)^{r-1}1^1+...+C_r^{r-1}(k_1m)^11^{r-1}+C_r^r(k_1m)^01^r]\ mod\ m =\ C_r^r(k_1m)^01^r\ mod\ m=1\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[\therefore (g^a)^r\equiv 1(mod\ m)\\\]</span></p><p>同理可得： <span class="math display">\[(g^b)^s\equiv 1(mod\ m)\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[\therefore (g^a)^r·(g^b)^s \equiv 1(mod\ m) \Leftrightarrowg^{ar＋bs}\equiv1(mod\ m)\Leftrightarrow g^{gcd(a,b)}\equiv1(mod\ m)\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[Ⅱ.当m=1\]</span></p><p>易知： <span class="math display">\[g^{gcd(a,b)}\ mod\ 1=0\]</span> 又 <span class="math display">\[1\ mod\ 1=0\]</span> 故 <span class="math display">\[g^{gcd(a,b)}\equiv1(mod\ m)\]</span> Q.E.D</p><h2 id="第8题">4.2 第8题</h2><ul><li><spanclass="math display">\[证明：如果gcd(a,b)=d,则gcd(a/d,b/d)=1\]</span></li></ul><hr /><p>证明：</p><p><span class="math display">\[\because gcd(a,b)=d\]</span>可知a与b的最大公因数为d。</p><p><span class="math display">\[Ⅰ.当a\neq b时\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[设\exists t_1,t_2 \in Z\ 且 t_1\neq t_2\neq 0\ ,\ s.t.\]</span> <span class="math display">\[a=t_1d\\b=t_2d\\\]</span> <span class="math display">\[假设gcd(t_1,t_2)=k\neq1,则必\exists d^* = kd,s.t.\ d^*&gt;d,与题意不符\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[即t_1与t_2互素\]</span></p><p>又： <span class="math display">\[a/d = t_1\\b/d = t_2\]</span> <span class="math display">\[故gcd(a/d,b/d)=1\]</span>。</p><p><span class="math display">\[Ⅱ.当a=b时\]</span></p><p>易知：<span class="math display">\[a=b=d\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[则gcd(a/d,b/d)= gcd(1,1)=1\]</span></p><p>Q.E.D</p>]]></content>
    
    
